title: NFL ATL: Week 9 preview, TNF recap
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 9 preview, TNF recap
description:
A room full of heroes, Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Chris Wesseling gear up to give you a full Week 9 preview and break down the top games to watch. The crew also recaps all of the action from the “Thursday Night Football” matchup between the Cincinnati Bengals and the Miami Dolphins. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
